Here are the complete findings for all five search items:

---

## 1. FilterView-related RPC Procedures in `src/rpc/router/`

**File:** `/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/src/rpc/router/filter-view.ts` (full file, 20 lines)

```ts
import { eq } from "drizzle-orm";
import { z } from "zod";

import { filterViews } from "@/db-schemas";
import { db } from "@/lib/db/server";
import { protectedProcedure } from "@/rpc/middleware";

const listFilterViewsSchema = z.object({
  domain: z.string(),
});

export const filterViewList = protectedProcedure
  .meta({ permission: { action: "read", resource: "filter_views" } })
  .input(listFilterViewsSchema)
  .handler(async ({ input }) => {
    return db
      .select()
      .from(filterViews)
      .where(eq(filterViews.domain, input.domain));
  });
```

**Status: Only `list` exists. There are NO `create`, `update`, or `delete` procedures for filterView.** Only `filterViewList` is exported.

