## Summary of Gaps

The filterView feature is **partially implemented**:

| Layer | Status |
|---|---|
| DB Schema | Present — `src/db-schemas/filter-view.ts` |
| DB Schema Index | Exported — `src/db-schemas/index.ts` line 4 |
| Service Layer | **Missing** — no `src/services/filter-view-service.ts` |
| RPC Router | Partial — only `list` exists in `src/rpc/router/filter-view.ts` |
